Charlotte Salt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charlotte_Salt 0 Charlotte Salt (born 1985) is an English actress best known for her many characters in British and US television series like Casualty, Bedlam and The Musketeers, also in many movies, including Beneath Still Waters in 2005, Beowulf in 2007, and Blood and Glory in 2016.
